    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road? I\u2019m selling my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-maintained, so it still runs smoothly and looks great! It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve loved driving this beauty, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
